"Nobody's pointed out that she's the first planeswalker you can drop turn 1 with Dark Ritual? She is probably breakable, for that reason alone." ~ steev  

@steev - Actually that honor goes to [Jace Beleren](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace Beleren), via [Black Lotus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Black Lotus). Unless you want to bring the Moxen and Tolarian academy into the picture, in which case, you would be able to play any planeswalker turn 1. :3  

That said, this card is nice, although she will have a hefty price tag for a while. Here's hoping for lucky pulls, at least until I get a job..
